        ],
        "Contractor|AssassinationDescription": [
            "Never trust a screw not to twist. One of the BlacJac officers who\u2019s supposed to be looking after our interests is taking a double dip and working for another crew. Can\u2019t have that. \n\nHunt down Officer ~mission(TargetName) and take care of it. Just be ready for a hard fight from all their BlacJac friends.\n\n-Twitch",
            "A BlacJac officer by the name of ~mission(TargetName) has put it in their mind that they\u2019re going to be a hero and put a stop to our operation once and for all. \n\nProblem is that this shiner is smart and motivated enough to be an actual threat. \n\nWe need them stopped dead in their tracks before something sticks. And I don\u2019t care how many BlacJacs you have to cut down to see it through.\n\n-Twitch",
            "~mission(TargetName), a long time BlacJac officer on our payroll, suddenly decided to grow a conscience and the new look doesn\u2019t suit them at all. \n\nWe need ~mission(TargetName|Last) silenced before they have a chance to come clean.\n\nTake care of them and any BlacJacs that want to come along for the ride.\n\n-Twitch",
            "Don\u2019t get me wrong, I love credits as much as the next person, but loyalty has a value beyond money. \n\nOfficer ~mission(TargetName) has decided that we aren\u2019t paying them enough and is threatening to let their BlacJac bosses in on some of our business dealings.\n\nYou\u2019re going to go put and end to this bastard\u2019s greed once and for all. \n\nDon\u2019t be surprised if they run crying to BlacJac for help once the shooting starts. Just do what you have to and get it done.\n\n-Twitch"
        ],
        "Contractor": [
            "Tecia Pacheco"
        ]
    },
